          Lets settle few things first-<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span><br />
          I didn't purchased @ B&amp;M store,so YES! there's no manufacturer warranty, but that's obvious, for price I paid,no auth. TH seller would match..so if it's a brick..then its my loss.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span><br />
